{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882172672,"sessionID":"ses_2852cba5effeAuUCCl0SevNMJl","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad369b5001mUbuzgM2O6d5RO","messageID":"msg_d7ad35ad0001lB44PbOF4BTi0A","sessionID":"ses_2852cba5effeAuUCCl0SevNMJl","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_3907b51b7d2a4e92a5559f07","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/Makefile"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/Makefile</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Makefile for AgentCube Docker builds\n2: # Provides targets for building, pushing, and managing container images\n3: \n4: # Docker configuration\n5: DOCKER_REGISTRY ?= ghcr.io/volcano-sh\n6: DOCKER_TAG ?= latest\n7: VERSION ?= $(shell git describe --tags --always --dirty 2>/dev/null || echo \"dev\")\n8: COMMIT_SHA ?= $(shell git rev-parse --short HEAD 2>/dev/null || echo \"unknown\")\n9: \n10: # Image names\n11: WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/workloadmanager\n12: ROUTER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/router\n13: PICOD_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/picod\n14: \n15: # Build all images\n16: .PHONY: docker-build-all\n17: docker-build-all: docker-build-workloadmanager docker-build-router docker-build-picod\n18: \t@echo \"✓ All images built successfully\"\n19: \n20: # Build Workload Manager image\n21: .PHONY: docker-build-workloadmanager\n22: docker-build-workloadmanager:\n23: \t@echo \"Building Workload Manager image...\"\n24: \tdocker build \\\n25: \t\t-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile \\\n26: \t\t--build-arg VERSION=$(VERSION) \\\n27: \t\t--build-arg COMMIT_SHA=$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n28: \t\t-t $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n29: \t\t-t $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n30: \t\t-t $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(VERSION) \\\n31: \t\t.\n32: \t@echo \"✓ Workload Manager image built: $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\"\n33: \n34: # Build Router image\n35: .PHONY: docker-build-router\n36: docker-build-router:\n37: \t@echo \"Building Router image...\"\n38: \tdocker build \\\n39: \t\t-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile.router \\\n40: \t\t--build-arg VERSION=$(VERSION) \\\n41: \t\t--build-arg COMMIT_SHA=$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n42: \t\t-t $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n43: \t\t-t $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n44: \t\t-t $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(VERSION) \\\n45: \t\t.\n46: \t@echo \"✓ Router image built: $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\"\n47: \n48: # Build Picod image\n49: .PHONY: docker-build-picod\n50: docker-build-picod:\n51: \t@echo \"Building Picod image...\"\n52: \tdocker build \\\n53: \t\t-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile.picod \\\n54: \t\t--build-arg VERSION=$(VERSION) \\\n55: \t\t--build-arg COMMIT_SHA=$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n56: \t\t-t $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n57: \t\t-t $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n58: \t\t-t $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(VERSION) \\\n59: \t\t.\n60: \t@echo \"✓ Picod image built: $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\"\n61: \n62: # Push all images\n63: .PHONY: docker-push-all\n64: docker-push-all: docker-push-workloadmanager docker-push-router docker-push-picod\n65: \t@echo \"✓ All images pushed successfully\"\n66: \n67: # Push Workload Manager image\n68: .PHONY: docker-push-workloadmanager\n69: docker-push-workloadmanager:\n70: \t@echo \"Pushing Workload Manager image to $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)...\"\n71: \tdocker push $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n72: \tdocker push $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA)\n73: \tdocker push $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(VERSION)\n74: \n75: # Push Router image\n76: .PHONY: docker-push-router\n77: docker-push-router:\n78: \t@echo \"Pushing Router image to $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)...\"\n79: \tdocker push $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n80: \tdocker push $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA)\n81: \tdocker push $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(VERSION)\n82: \n83: # Push Picod image\n84: .PHONY: docker-push-picod\n85: docker-push-picod:\n86: \t@echo \"Pushing Picod image to $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)...\"\n87: \tdocker push $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n88: \tdocker push $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA)\n89: \tdocker push $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(VERSION)\n90: \n91: # Load images to Kind cluster\n92: .PHONY: kind-load-all\n93: kind-load-all: kind-load-workloadmanager kind-load-router kind-load-picod\n94: \t@echo \"✓ All images loaded to Kind cluster\"\n95: \n96: .PHONY: kind-load-workloadmanager\n97: kind-load-workloadmanager:\n98: \tkind load docker-image $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n99: \n100: .PHONY: kind-load-router\n101: kind-load-router:\n102: \tkind load docker-image $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n103: \n104: .PHONY: kind-load-picod\n105: kind-load-picod:\n106: \tkind load docker-image $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n107: \n108: # Multi-architecture build (requires Docker Buildx)\n109: .PHONY: docker-buildx-all\n110: docker-buildx-all: docker-buildx-workloadmanager docker-buildx-router docker-buildx-picod\n111: \t@echo \"✓ All multi-arch images built successfully\"\n112: \n113: .PHONY: docker-buildx-workloadmanager\n114: docker-buildx-workloadmanager:\n115: \t@echo \"Building multi-arch Workload Manager image...\"\n116: \tdocker buildx build \\\n117: \t\t--platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64 \\\n118: \t\t-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile \\\n119: \t\t--build-arg VERSION=$(VERSION) \\\n120: \t\t--build-arg COMMIT_SHA=$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n121: \t\t-t $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n122: \t\t--push \\\n123: \t\t.\n124: \n125: .PHONY: docker-buildx-router\n126: docker-buildx-router:\n127: \t@echo \"Building multi-arch Router image...\"\n128: \tdocker buildx build \\\n129: \t\t--platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64 \\\n130: \t\t-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile.router \\\n131: \t\t--build-arg VERSION=$(VERSION) \\\n132: \t\t--build-arg COMMIT_SHA=$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n133: \t\t-t $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n134: \t\t--push \\\n135: \t\t.\n136: \n137: .PHONY: docker-buildx-picod\n138: docker-buildx-picod:\n139: \t@echo \"Building multi-arch Picod image...\"\n140: \tdocker buildx build \\\n141: \t\t--platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64 \\\n142: \t\t-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile.picod \\\n143: \t\t--build-arg VERSION=$(VERSION) \\\n144: \t\t--build-arg COMMIT_SHA=$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n145: \t\t-t $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n146: \t\t--push \\\n147: \t\t.\n148: \n149: # Clean up local images\n150: .PHONY: docker-clean\n151: docker-clean:\n152: \t@echo \"Cleaning up local Docker images...\"\n153: \t-docker rmi $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) 2>/dev/null || true\n154: \t-docker rmi $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) 2>/dev/null || true\n155: \t-docker rmi $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(VERSION) 2>/dev/null || true\n156: \t-docker rmi $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) 2>/dev/null || true\n157: \t-docker rmi $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) 2>/dev/null || true\n158: \t-docker rmi $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(VERSION) 2>/dev/null || true\n159: \t-docker rmi $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) 2>/dev/null || true\n160: \t-docker rmi $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) 2>/dev/null || true\n161: \t-docker rmi $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(VERSION) 2>/dev/null || true\n162: \t@echo \"✓ Cleanup complete\"\n163: \n164: # Validate images (size, security, configuration)\n165: .PHONY: docker-validate\n166: docker-validate: docker-validate-workloadmanager docker-validate-router docker-validate-picod\n167: \t@echo \"✓ All images validated successfully\"\n168: \n169: .PHONY: docker-validate-workloadmanager\n170: docker-validate-workloadmanager:\n171: \t@echo \"Validating Workload Manager image...\"\n172: \t@./deployment/docker/test/validate.sh $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n173: \n174: .PHONY: docker-validate-router\n175: docker-validate-router:\n176: \t@echo \"Validating Router image...\"\n177: \t@./deployment/docker/test/validate.sh $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n178: \n179: .PHONY: docker-validate-picod\n180: docker-validate-picod:\n181: \t@echo \"Validating Picod image...\"\n182: \t@./deployment/docker/test/validate.sh $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n183: \n184: # Run all tests\n185: .PHONY: docker-test\n186: docker-test: docker-test-build docker-test-runtime\n187: \t@echo \"✓ All Docker tests passed\"\n188: \n189: .PHONY: docker-test-build\n190: docker-test-build:\n191: \t@echo \"Running build tests...\"\n192: \t@./deployment/docker/test/build_test.sh\n193: \n194: .PHONY: docker-test-runtime\n195: docker-test-runtime:\n196: \t@echo \"Running runtime tests...\"\n197: \t@./deployment/docker/test/runtime_test.sh\n198: \n199: # Help target\n200: .PHONY: help\n201: help:\n202: \t@echo \"AgentCube Docker Makefile\"\n203: \t@echo \"\"\n204: \t@echo \"Build targets:\"\n205: \t@echo \"  docker-build-all              - Build all three images\"\n206: \t@echo \"  docker-build-workloadmanager  - Build Workload Manager image\"\n207: \t@echo \"  docker-build-router           - Build Router image\"\n208: \t@echo \"  docker-build-picod            - Build Picod image\"\n209: \t@echo \"\"\n210: \t@echo \"Push targets:\"\n211: \t@echo \"  docker-push-all               - Push all images to registry\"\n212: \t@echo \"  docker-push-workloadmanager   - Push Workload Manager image\"\n213: \t@echo \"  docker-push-router            - Push Router image\"\n214: \t@echo \"  docker-push-picod             - Push Picod image\"\n215: \t@echo \"\"\n216: \t@echo \"Kind targets:\"\n217: \t@echo \"  kind-load-all                 - Load all images to Kind cluster\"\n218: \t@echo \"  kind-load-workloadmanager     - Load Workload Manager image\"\n219: \t@echo \"  kind-load-router              - Load Router image\"\n220: \t@echo \"  kind-load-picod               - Load Picod image\"\n221: \t@echo \"\"\n222: \t@echo \"Multi-arch targets:\"\n223: \t@echo \"  docker-buildx-all             - Build multi-arch images (amd64, arm64)\"\n224: \t@echo \"  docker-buildx-workloadmanager - Build multi-arch Workload Manager\"\n225: \t@echo \"  docker-buildx-router          - Build multi-arch Router\"\n226: \t@echo \"  docker-buildx-picod           - Build multi-arch Picod\"\n227: \t@echo \"\"\n228: \t@echo \"Test & validate targets:\"\n229: \t@echo \"  docker-test                   - Run all Docker tests\"\n230: \t@echo \"  docker-validate               - Validate all images\"\n231: \t@echo \"  docker-clean                  - Clean up local images\"\n232: \t@echo \"\"\n233: \t@echo \"Variables:\"\n234: \t@echo \"  DOCKER_REGISTRY=$(DOCKER_REGISTRY)\"\n235: \t@echo \"  DOCKER_TAG=$(DOCKER_TAG)\"\n236: \t@echo \"  VERSION=$(VERSION)\"\n237: \t@echo \"  COMMIT_SHA=$(COMMIT_SHA)\"\n\n(End of file - total 237 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Makefile for AgentCube Docker builds\n# Provides targets for building, pushing, and managing container images\n\n# Docker configuration\nDOCKER_REGISTRY ?= ghcr.io/volcano-sh\nDOCKER_TAG ?= latest\nVERSION ?= $(shell git describe --tags --always --dirty 2>/dev/null || echo \"dev\")\nCOMMIT_SHA ?= $(shell git rev-parse --short HEAD 2>/dev/null || echo \"unknown\")\n\n# Image names\nWORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/workloadmanager\nROUTER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/router\nPICOD_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/picod\n\n# Build all images\n.PHONY: docker-build-all\ndocker-build-all: docker-build-workloadmanager docker-build-router docker-build-picod\n\t@echo \"✓ All images built successfully\"\n\n# Build Workload Manager image","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/Makefile","time":{"start":1775882172647,"end":1775882172670}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882172676,"sessionID":"ses_2852cba5effeAuUCCl0SevNMJl","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad36ec4001w09phG5aiJn2QF","messageID":"msg_d7ad35ad0001lB44PbOF4BTi0A","sessionID":"ses_2852cba5effeAuUCCl0SevNMJl","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_f83443e0ca514370a5e3b274","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-033/index.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-033/index.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-033 — Makefile 构建目标体系\n2: \n3: **Module:** root  \n4: **Language:** Makefile  \n5: **Size:** M  \n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## Status\n10: - [ ] Spec written\n11: - [ ] Plan approved\n12: - [ ] Code complete\n13: - [ ] Review passed\n14: - [ ] Merged\n15: \n16: ---\n17: \n18: ## Links\n19: - [Spec](./spec/)\n20: - [Plan](./plan/)\n21: - [Worktree](./worktree/)\n22: - [Review Notes](./review-notes/)\n\n(End of file - total 22 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-033 — Makefile 构建目标体系\n\n**Module:** root  \n**Language:** Makefile  \n**Size:** M  \n\n---\n\n## Status\n- [ ] Spec written\n- [ ] Plan approved\n- [ ] Code complete\n- [ ] Review passed\n- [ ] Merged\n\n---\n\n## Links\n- [Spec](./spec/)\n- [Plan](./plan/)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-033/index.md","time":{"start":1775882172652,"end":1775882172675}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882172680,"sessionID":"ses_2852cba5effeAuUCCl0SevNMJl","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad373d2001s8uteoXx9S7hXd","messageID":"msg_d7ad35ad0001lB44PbOF4BTi0A","sessionID":"ses_2852cba5effeAuUCCl0SevNMJl","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_2e9c7b84a81644d7a29ef544","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-032/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-032/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images)\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 Dockerfile 多阶段构建，为 Workload Manager、Router、Volcano Agent Scheduler 三个核心组件提供独立的容器镜像构建能力。该 Dockerfile 是 AgentCube 控制平面组件容器化的基础，支撑 Helm Chart 部署和 Kubernetes 运行时环境。\n6: \n7: 目标是：\n8: \n9: 1. **多阶段构建优化** - 使用多阶段构建减少最终镜像体积，仅包含运行必需的二进制文件和配置\n10: 2. **三镜像分离** - 为 Workload Manager、Router、Volcano Agent Scheduler 分别构建独立镜像，支持差异化部署\n11: 3. **最小化攻击面** - 基于 distroless 或 alpine 基础镜像，减少安全漏洞风险\n12: 4. **构建可复用** - 统一的 Dockerfile 模板支持本地构建、CI/CD 流水线、多架构支持\n13: 5. **环境一致性** - 确保开发、测试、生产环境的镜像构建行为一致\n14: 6. **版本可追溯** - 镜像标签与 Git commit/Tag 关联，支持版本追踪和回滚\n15: \n16: 本提案基于 deployment/design.md 和 deployment/spec.md 的规范，遵循 Docker 多阶段构建最佳实践。\n17: \n18: ## Scope\n19: \n20: **Module:** docker  \n21: **Language:** Dockerfile  \n22: **Size:** S\n23: \n24: 本 AR 包含：\n25: \n26: - **包含内容：**\n27:   - Dockerfile.workloadmanager - Workload Manager 镜像构建\n28:   - Dockerfile.router - Router 镜像构建\n29:   - Dockerfile.volcano-agent-scheduler - Volcano Agent Scheduler 镜像构建\n30:   - .dockerignore 文件 - 构建上下文忽略规则\n31:   - Makefile 构建目标 - 简化镜像构建命令\n32:   - 镜像验证脚本 - 验证镜像大小、层数、安全性\n33:   - 构建文档和使用示例\n34: \n35: - **不包含内容：**\n36:   - Helm Chart 模板（由 AR-030 管理）\n37:   - Kubernetes 部署配置\n38:   - CI/CD 流水线配置\n39:   - 镜像仓库推送逻辑\n40: \n41: ## Current State Analysis\n42: \n43: ### 现有构建状态\n44: \n45: 根据项目结构 `cmd/` 目录：\n46: - `cmd/agentcube/` - Workload Manager 源码（Go）\n47: - `cmd/agentcube-admin/` - 管理工具（Go）\n48: - `cmd/agentcube-proxy/` - 代理服务（Go）\n49: - `cmd/agentcube-shell/` - Shell 工具（Go）\n50: - `cmd/agentd/` - Agent Daemon（Go，已有二进制文件）\n51: - `cmd/cli/` - CLI 工具（Python）\n52: \n53: 当前无 Dockerfile，缺少容器化构建能力。\n54: \n55: ### 参考设计规范\n56: \n57: 根据 `deployment/design.md` 和 `deployment/spec.md`：\n58: \n59: **镜像要求：**\n60: - Workload Manager: 基于 Go 二进制文件，暴露 8080 端口\n61: - Router: 基于 Go 二进制文件，暴露 8080 端口\n62: - Volcano Agent Scheduler: 基于 Go 二进制文件，暴露 8080 端口（metrics）\n63: \n64: **基础镜像要求：**\n65: - 生产镜像：使用 gcr.io/distroless/static-debian11 或 alpine:3.18\n66: - 构建镜像：使用 golang:1.21-bookworm\n67: \n68: **镜像标签规范：**\n69: - latest - 最新开发版本\n70: - <version> - 语义化版本（如 0.1.0）\n71: - <commit-sha> - Git commit SHA\n72: \n73: ### 差距分析\n74: \n75: 1. **缺少 Dockerfile** - 无任何 Dockerfile，无法构建容器镜像\n76: 2. **缺少构建优化** - 未使用多阶段构建，镜像体积可能过大\n77: 3. **缺少安全加固** - 未使用 distroless 或最小化基础镜像\n78: 4. **缺少构建自动化** - 无 Makefile 构建目标或脚本\n79: \n80: ### deployment/spec.md 关键要求\n81: \n82: 1. **镜像分离** - 每个组件独立镜像，避免耦合\n83: 2. **端口暴露** - Workload Manager 8080, Router 8080, Scheduler 8080 (metrics)\n84: 3. **环境变量** - 支持 REDIS_ADDR, REDIS_PASSWORD, AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE 等\n85: 4. **健康检查** - Docker HEALTHCHECK 指令配置\n86: 5. **非 root 用户** - 生产镜像以非 root 用户运行\n87: \n88: ## Proposed Changes\n89: \n90: ### 1. 目录结构\n91: \n92: ```\n93: docker/\n94: ├── .dockerignore                       # 构建上下文忽略\n95: ├── Dockerfile.workloadmanager          # Workload Manager Dockerfile\n96: ├── Dockerfile.router                   # Router Dockerfile\n97: ├── Dockerfile.volcano-agent-scheduler  # Volcano Agent Scheduler Dockerfile\n98: ├── Makefile                            # 构建目标\n99: ├── validate.sh                         # 镜像验证脚本\n100: └── README.md                           # 构建说明文档\n101: ```\n102: \n103: ### 2. .dockerignore\n104: \n105: ```dockerignore\n106: # .dockerignore\n107: # Build context ignores\n108: \n109: # Git\n110: .git\n111: .gitignore\n112: \n113: # Build artifacts\n114: bin/\n115: dist/\n116: *.out\n117: \n118: # Dependencies\n119: vendor/\n120: \n121: # IDE\n122: .idea/\n123: .vscode/\n124: *.swp\n125: *.swo\n126: \n127: # Documentation\n128: *.md\n129: !README.md\n130: \n131: # Tests\n132: testing/\n133: *_test.go\n134: \n135: # Docker\n136: docker/\n137: Dockerfile*\n138: \n139: # Helm\n140: manifests/\n141: \n142: # Python\n143: __pycache__/\n144: *.pyc\n145: .pytest_cache/\n146: \n147: # Misc\n148: .DS_Store\n149: Thumbs.db\n150: ```\n151: \n152: ### 3. Workload Manager Dockerfile\n153: \n154: ```dockerfile\n155: # docker/Dockerfile.workloadmanager\n156: # Multi-stage build for Workload Manager\n157: \n158: # Stage 1: Build\n159: FROM golang:1.21-bookworm AS builder\n160: \n161: WORKDIR /build\n162: \n163: # Copy go mod files\n164: COPY go.mod go.sum ./\n165: RUN go mod download\n166: \n167: # Copy source code\n168: COPY cmd/agentcube ./cmd/agentcube\n169: COPY pkg ./pkg\n170: \n171: # Build the binary\n172: RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build \\\n173:     -ldflags=\"-w -s\" \\\n174:     -o /build/workloadmanager \\\n175:     ./cmd/agentcube\n176: \n177: # Stage 2: Runtime (distroless)\n178: FROM gcr.io/distroless/static-debian11:nonroot AS runtime\n179: \n180: # Copy binary from builder\n181: COPY --from=builder /build/workloadmanager /workloadmanager\n182: \n183: # Set non-root user\n184: USER nonroot:nonroot\n185: \n186: # Set working directory\n187: WORKDIR /\n188: \n189: # Expose port\n190: EXPOSE 8080\n191: \n192: # Health check\n193: HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \\\n194:     CMD [\"/workloadmanager\", \"--health\"]\n195: \n196: # Entrypoint\n197: ENTRYPOINT [\"/workloadmanager\"]\n198: CMD [\"--port=8080\"]\n199: ```\n200: \n201: ### 4. Router Dockerfile\n202: \n203: ```dockerfile\n204: # docker/Dockerfile.router\n205: # Multi-stage build for Router\n206: \n207: # Stage 1: Build\n208: FROM golang:1.21-bookworm AS builder\n209: \n210: WORKDIR /build\n211: \n212: # Copy go mod files\n213: COPY go.mod go.sum ./\n214: RUN go mod download\n215: \n216: # Copy source code\n217: COPY cmd/agentcube-proxy ./cmd/agentcube-proxy\n218: COPY pkg ./pkg\n219: \n220: # Build the binary\n221: RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build \\\n222:     -ldflags=\"-w -s\" \\\n223:     -o /build/router \\\n224:     ./cmd/agentcube-proxy\n225: \n226: # Stage 2: Runtime (distroless)\n227: FROM gcr.io/distroless/static-debian11:nonroot AS runtime\n228: \n229: # Copy binary from builder\n230: COPY --from=builder /build/router /router\n231: \n232: # Set non-root user\n233: USER nonroot:nonroot\n234: \n235: # Set working directory\n236: WORKDIR /\n237: \n238: # Expose port\n239: EXPOSE 8080\n240: \n241: # Health check\n242: HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \\\n243:     CMD [\"/router\", \"--health\"]\n244: \n245: # Entrypoint\n246: ENTRYPOINT [\"/router\"]\n247: CMD [\"--port=8080\", \"--debug\"]\n248: ```\n249: \n250: ### 5. Volcano Agent Scheduler Dockerfile\n251: \n252: ```dockerfile\n253: # docker/Dockerfile.volcano-agent-scheduler\n254: # Multi-stage build for Volcano Agent Scheduler\n255: \n256: # Stage 1: Build\n257: FROM golang:1.21-bookworm AS builder\n258: \n259: WORKDIR /build\n260: \n261: # Copy go mod files\n262: COPY go.mod go.sum ./\n263: RUN go mod download\n264: \n265: # Copy source code\n266: COPY cmd/agentd ./cmd/agentd\n267: COPY pkg ./pkg\n268: \n269: # Build the binary\n270: RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build \\\n271:     -ldflags=\"-w -s\" \\\n272:     -o /build/volcano-agent-scheduler \\\n273:     ./cmd/agentd\n274: \n275: # Stage 2: Runtime (distroless)\n276: FROM gcr.io/distroless/static-debian11:nonroot AS runtime\n277: \n278: # Copy binary from builder\n279: COPY --from=builder /build/volcano-agent-scheduler /volcano-agent-scheduler\n280: \n281: # Copy default config\n282: COPY sandbox-orchestration/agent-scheduler.conf /config/agent-scheduler.conf\n283: \n284: # Set non-root user\n285: USER nonroot:nonroot\n286: \n287: # Set working directory\n288: WORKDIR /\n289: \n290: # Expose metrics port\n291: EXPOSE 8080\n292: \n293: # Health check\n294: HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \\\n295:     CMD [\"/volcano-agent-scheduler\", \"--health\"]\n296: \n297: # Entrypoint\n298: ENTRYPOINT [\"/volcano-agent-scheduler\"]\n299: CMD [\"--scheduler-name=agent-scheduler\", \"--config=/config/agent-scheduler.conf\"]\n300: ```\n301: \n302: ### 6. Makefile Build Targets\n303: \n304: ```makefile\n305: # Makefile (add to root or docker/Makefile)\n306: \n307: # Docker build configuration\n308: DOCKER_REGISTRY ?= ghcr.io/volcano-sh\n309: DOCKER_TAG ?= latest\n310: VERSION ?= $(shell git describe --tags --always --dirty)\n311: COMMIT_SHA ?= $(shell git rev-parse --short HEAD)\n312: \n313: # Image names\n314: WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/workloadmanager\n315: ROUTER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/agentcube-router\n316: VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/vc-agent-scheduler\n317: \n318: # Build targets\n319: .PHONY: docker-build\n320: docker-build: docker-build-workloadmanager docker-build-router docker-build-scheduler\n321: \n322: .PHONY: docker-build-workloadmanager\n323: docker-build-workloadmanager:\n324: \tdocker build \\\n325: \t\t-f docker/Dockerfile.workloadmanager \\\n326: \t\t-t $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n327: \t\t-t $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n328: \t\t.\n329: \n330: .PHONY: docker-build-router\n331: docker-build-router:\n332: \tdocker build \\\n333: \t\t-f docker/Dockerfile.router \\\n334: \t\t-t $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n335: \t\t-t $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n336: \t\t.\n337: \n338: .PHONY: docker-build-scheduler\n339: docker-build-scheduler:\n340: \tdocker build \\\n341: \t\t-f docker/Dockerfile.volcano-agent-scheduler \\\n342: \t\t-t $(VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n343: \t\t-t $(VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n344: \t\t.\n345: \n346: .PHONY: docker-push\n347: docker-push: docker-push-workloadmanager docker-push-router docker-push-scheduler\n348: \n349: .PHONY: docker-push-workloadmanager\n350: docker-push-workloadmanager:\n351: \tdocker push $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n352: \tdocker push $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA)\n353: \n354: .PHONY: docker-push-router\n355: docker-push-router:\n356: \tdocker push $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n357: \tdocker push $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA)\n358: \n359: .PHONY: docker-push-scheduler\n360: docker-push-scheduler:\n361: \tdocker push $(VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n362: \tdocker push $(VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA)\n363: \n364: .PHONY: docker-validate\n365: docker-validate:\n366: \t./docker/validate.sh\n367: \n368: .PHONY: docker-clean\n369: docker-clean:\n370: \tdocker rmi $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) 2>/dev/null || true\n371: \tdocker rmi $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) 2>/dev/null || true\n372: \tdocker rmi $(VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) 2>/dev/null || true\n373: ```\n374: \n375: ### 7. 镜像验证脚本\n376: \n377: ```bash\n378: #!/bin/bash\n379: # docker/validate.sh\n380: \n381: set -e\n382: \n383: WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE=\"${DOCKER_REGISTRY:-ghcr.io/volcano-sh}/workloadmanager:${DOCKER_TAG:-latest}\"\n384: ROUTER_IMAGE=\"${DOCKER_REGISTRY:-ghcr.io/volcano-sh}/agentcube-router:${DOCKER_TAG:-latest}\"\n385: VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE=\"${DOCKER_REGISTRY:-ghcr.io/volcano-sh}/vc-agent-scheduler:${DOCKER_TAG:-latest}\"\n386: \n387: echo \"Validating Docker images...\"\n388: echo \"\"\n389: \n390: # Function to check image\n391: check_image() {\n392:     local image=$1\n393:     local name=$2\n394:     \n395:     echo \"Checking $name...\"\n396:     \n397:     # Check if image exists\n398:     if ! docker image inspect \"$image\" > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n399:         echo \"  ✗ Image not found: $image\"\n400:         return 1\n401:     fi\n402:     echo \"  ✓ Image exists\"\n403:     \n404:     # Check image size (should be < 50MB for distroless)\n405:     local size=$(docker image inspect \"$image\" --format='{{.Size}}')\n406:     local size_mb=$((size / 1024 / 1024))\n407:     if [ $size_mb -lt 50 ]; then\n408:         echo \"  ✓ Image size: ${size_mb}MB (< 50MB)\"\n409:     else\n410:         echo \"  ✗ Image size: ${size_mb}MB (>= 50MB)\"\n411:         return 1\n412:     fi\n413:     \n414:     # Check layer count (should be <= 5)\n415:     local layers=$(docker image history \"$image\" --format='{{.ID}}' | wc -l)\n416:     if [ $layers -le 5 ]; then\n417:         echo \"  ✓ Layer count: $layers (<= 5)\"\n418:     else\n419:         echo \"  ✗ Layer count: $layers (> 5)\"\n420:         return 1\n421:     fi\n422:     \n423:     # Check if running as non-root\n424:     local user=$(docker image inspect \"$image\" --format='{{.Config.User}}')\n425:     if [ -n \"$user\" ] && [ \"$user\" != \"root\" ]; then\n426:         echo \"  ✓ Running as non-root: $user\"\n427:     else\n428:         echo \"  ✗ Running as root or no user specified\"\n429:         return 1\n430:     fi\n431:     \n432:     # Check exposed ports\n433:     local ports=$(docker image inspect \"$image\" --format='{{json .Config.ExposedPorts}}')\n434:     if echo \"$ports\" | grep -q \"8080\"; then\n435:         echo \"  ✓ Port 8080 exposed\"\n436:     else\n437:         echo \"  ✗ Port 8080 not exposed\"\n438:         return 1\n439:     fi\n440:     \n441:     # Check health check\n442:     local healthcheck=$(docker image inspect \"$image\" --format='{{json .Config.Healthcheck}}')\n443:     if [ \"$healthcheck\" != \"null\" ] && [ -n \"$healthcheck\" ]; then\n444:         echo \"  ✓ Health check configured\"\n445:     else\n446:         echo \"  ✗ Health check not configured\"\n447:         return 1\n448:     fi\n449:     \n450:     echo \"\"\n451: }\n452: \n453: # Validate all images\n454: check_image \"$WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE\" \"Workload Manager\"\n455: check_image \"$ROUTER_IMAGE\" \"Router\"\n456: check_image \"$VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE\" \"Volcano Agent Scheduler\"\n457: \n458: echo \"All validations passed!\"\n459: ```\n460: \n461: ### 8. 构建文档 (docker/README.md)\n462: \n463: ```markdown\n464: # Docker Image Builds\n465: \n466: AgentCube 控制平面组件的 Docker 镜像构建配置。\n467: \n468: ## 镜像列表\n469: \n470: | 组件 | 镜像名 | 端口 | 大小目标 |\n471: |------|--------|------|----------|\n472: | Workload Manager | ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager | 8080 | < 50MB |\n473: | Router | ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router | 8080 | < 50MB |\n474: | Volcano Agent Scheduler | ghcr.io/volcano-sh/vc-agent-scheduler | 8080 | < 50MB |\n475: \n476: ## 快速开始\n477: \n478: ### 构建所有镜像\n479: \n480: ```bash\n481: make docker-build\n482: ```\n483: \n484: ### 构建单个镜像\n485: \n486: ```bash\n487: make docker-build-workloadmanager\n488: make docker-build-router\n489: make docker-build-scheduler\n490: ```\n491: \n492: ### 推送镜像\n493: \n494: ```bash\n495: make docker-push\n496: ```\n497: \n498: ### 验证镜像\n499: \n500: ```bash\n501: make docker-validate\n502: ```\n503: \n504: ## 自定义配置\n505: \n506: ### 修改镜像仓库\n507: \n508: ```bash\n509: export DOCKER_REGISTRY=myregistry.com\n510: make docker-build\n511: ```\n512: \n513: ### 修改镜像标签\n514: \n515: ```bash\n516: export DOCKER_TAG=v0.1.0\n517: make docker-build\n518: ```\n519: \n520: ## 多架构支持\n521: \n522: ```bash\n523: docker buildx build \\\n524:   --platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64 \\\n525:   -t ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager:latest \\\n526:   --push \\\n527:   -f docker/Dockerfile.workloadmanager \\\n528:   .\n529: ```\n530: \n531: ## 安全最佳实践\n532: \n533: 1. **非 root 用户** - 所有镜像以 nonroot 用户运行\n534: 2. **Distroless 基础** - 使用 distroless/static-debian11 减少攻击面\n535: 3. **多阶段构建** - 仅复制必需的二进制文件\n536: 4. **静态链接** - CGO_ENABLED=0 避免动态库依赖\n537: 5. **健康检查** - 配置 HEALTHCHECK 指令\n538: \n539: ## 故障排查\n540: \n541: ### 镜像构建失败\n542: \n543: 检查 Go 代码是否能编译：\n544: ```bash\n545: go build -o /tmp/test ./cmd/agentcube\n546: ```\n547: \n548: ### 镜像过大\n549: \n550: 检查是否包含了不必要的文件：\n551: ```bash\n552: docker history <image-name>\n553: ```\n554: \n555: ### 权限错误\n556: \n557: 确保 Docker daemon 正常运行：\n558: ```bash\n559: docker info\n560: ```\n561: ```\n562: \n563: ## Impact Analysis\n564: \n565: ### 依赖影响\n566: \n567: | 依赖项 | 版本 | 用途 |\n568: |--------|------|------|\n569: | Docker | ≥20.10 | 镜像构建 |\n570: | Go | ≥1.21 | 应用编译 |\n571: | Make | 任意 | 构建自动化 |\n572: \n573: ### 模块依赖关系\n574: \n575: ```\n576: docker/\n577: ├── .dockerignore                       # 无依赖\n578: ├── Dockerfile.workloadmanager          # 依赖 cmd/agentcube, pkg/\n579: ├── Dockerfile.router                   # 依赖 cmd/agentcube-proxy, pkg/\n580: ├── Dockerfile.volcano-agent-scheduler  # 依赖 cmd/agentd, pkg/\n581: ├── Makefile                            # 依赖所有 Dockerfile\n582: ├── validate.sh                         # 依赖 docker CLI\n583: └── README.md                           # 文档\n584: ```\n585: \n586: ### 向后兼容性\n587: \n588: - 首次实现，无破坏性变更风险\n589: - 镜像标签策略支持版本追溯\n590: - 多架构支持未来扩展\n591: \n592: ### 测试影响\n593: \n594: - 需要验证镜像构建成功\n595: - 需要验证镜像大小符合目标\n596: - 需要验证容器可正常启动\n597: - 需要验证健康检查有效\n598: \n599: ## Alternatives Considered\n600: \n601: ### 方案 1: 单 Dockerfile 多目标构建\n602: \n603: **优点:**\n604: - 单一文件，易于维护\n605: - 使用 BUILDKIT 多目标\n606: \n607: **缺点:**\n608: - 文件过大，难以阅读\n609: - 不便于独立构建\n610: \n611: **决策:** 采用独立 Dockerfile，每个组件一个文件。\n612: \n613: ### 方案 2: 使用 Alpine 基础镜像\n614: \n615: **优点:**\n616: - 镜像体积小\n617: - 包管理方便\n618: \n619: **缺点:**\n620: - 存在已知安全漏洞\n621: - glibc 兼容性问题\n622: \n623: **决策:** 采用 distroless/static-debian11，更安全。\n624: \n625: ### 方案 3: 单一巨型镜像（包含所有组件）\n626: \n627: **优点:**\n628: - 单一镜像，部署简单\n629: - 减少镜像数量\n630: \n631: **缺点:**\n632: - 镜像体积大\n633: - 安全风险高\n634: - 无法独立部署组件\n635: \n636: **决策:** 采用独立镜像，支持最小化部署。\n637: \n638: ### 方案 4: 使用 Buildpacks\n639: \n640: **优点:**\n641: - 自动化程度高\n642: - 无需 Dockerfile\n643: \n644: **缺点:**\n645: - 定制化能力弱\n646: - 无法精确控制镜像内容\n647: \n648: **决策:** 采用 Dockerfile，保持完全控制。\n649: \n650: ## Testing Strategy\n651: \n652: ### 构建测试\n653: \n654: 1. **本地构建测试** - 验证所有 Dockerfile 可成功构建\n655: 2. **镜像大小测试** - 验证镜像体积 < 50MB\n656: 3. **层数测试** - 验证镜像层数 <= 5\n657: \n658: ### 功能测试\n659: \n660: 1. **容器启动测试** - 验证容器可正常启动\n661: 2. **健康检查测试** - 验证 HEALTHCHECK 有效\n662: 3. **端口暴露测试** - 验证 8080 端口可访问\n663: \n664: ### 安全测试\n665: \n666: 1. **非 root 测试** - 验证容器以非 root 用户运行\n667: 2. **漏洞扫描** - 使用 Trivy 扫描镜像漏洞\n668: 3. **最小权限测试** - 验证容器无多余权限\n669: \n670: ### 测试覆盖目标\n671: \n672: - Dockerfile: 100%（所有指令正确）\n673: - 构建脚本：100%（所有目标有效）\n674: - 验证脚本：100%（所有检查项通过）\n675: \n676: ## Acceptance Criteria\n677: \n678: - [ ] Workload Manager Dockerfile 可成功构建\n679: - [ ] Router Dockerfile 可成功构建\n680: - [ ] Volcano Agent Scheduler Dockerfile 可成功构建\n681: - [ ] 镜像大小 < 50MB\n682: - [ ] 镜像层数 <= 5\n683: - [ ] 容器以非 root 用户运行\n684: - [ ] 健康检查配置正确\n685: - [ ] 端口 8080 暴露\n686: - [ ] Makefile 构建目标可用\n687: - [ ] 验证脚本通过所有检查\n688: - [ ] 文档完整（构建说明、故障排查）\n689: \n690: ## Dependencies\n691: \n692: ### 必需依赖\n693: - Docker ≥20.10\n694: - Go ≥1.21\n695: - Make\n696: \n697: ### 可选依赖\n698: - Docker Buildx（多架构支持）\n699: - Trivy（安全扫描）\n700: \n701: ### 被依赖\n702: - AR-030 (Helm Chart) - 镜像用于 Helm Chart 部署\n703: - cmd/agentcube, cmd/agentcube-proxy, cmd/agentd - 应用源码\n704: \n705: ## Migration Notes\n706: \n707: ### 从手动构建迁移\n708: \n709: 1. 安装 Docker 和 Go 1.21+\n710: 2. 运行 `make docker-build` 构建镜像\n711: 3. 验证镜像 `make docker-validate`\n712: 4. 更新 Helm values.yaml 使用新镜像\n713: \n714: ### 破坏性变更\n715: 无 - 首次实现。\n716: \n717: ### 行为变更\n718: - 从源码编译改为容器化部署\n719: - 从直接运行改为容器运行\n720: \n721: ## Open Questions\n722: \n723: 1. 是否需要支持 Windows 容器？（未来扩展）\n724: 2. 是否需要集成镜像签名？（待需求明确）\n725: 3. 是否需要支持自定义基础镜像？（待需求明确）\n726: \n727: ## References\n728: \n729: - `deployment/spec.md` - 部署规范\n730: - `deployment/design.md` - 部署设计\n731: - `cmd/agentcube/` - Workload Manager 源码\n732: - `cmd/agentcube-proxy/` - Router 源码\n733: - `cmd/agentd/` - Volcano Agent Scheduler 源码\n734: - Docker Best Practices: https://docs.docker.com/develop/develop-images/dockerfile_best-practices/\n735: - Distroless Images: https://github.com/GoogleContainerTools/distroless\n\n(End of file - total 735 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images)\n\n## Purpose\n\n本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 Dockerfile 多阶段构建，为 Workload Manager、Router、Volcano Agent Scheduler 三个核心组件提供独立的容器镜像构建能力。该 Dockerfile 是 AgentCube 控制平面组件容器化的基础，支撑 Helm Chart 部署和 Kubernetes 运行时环境。\n\n目标是：\n\n1. **多阶段构建优化** - 使用多阶段构建减少最终镜像体积，仅包含运行必需的二进制文件和配置\n2. **三镜像分离** - 为 Workload Manager、Router、Volcano Agent Scheduler 分别构建独立镜像，支持差异化部署\n3. **最小化攻击面** - 基于 distroless 或 alpine 基础镜像，减少安全漏洞风险\n4. **构建可复用** - 统一的 Dockerfile 模板支持本地构建、CI/CD 流水线、多架构支持\n5. **环境一致性** - 确保开发、测试、生产环境的镜像构建行为一致\n6. **版本可追溯** - 镜像标签与 Git commit/Tag 关联，支持版本追踪和回滚\n\n本提案基于 deployment/design.md 和 deployment/spec.md 的规范，遵循 Docker 多阶段构建最佳实践。\n\n## Scope\n\n**Module:** docker  ","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-032/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775882172654,"end":1775882172677}}}}
