{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882268609,"sessionID":"ses_2852cba5effeAuUCCl0SevNMJl","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad3879a0019WmOxdy6v2jJ52","messageID":"msg_d7ad37940001oaeCbjr2UVf3lq","sessionID":"ses_2852cba5effeAuUCCl0SevNMJl","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_1806551595cb4709b732e42a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md","content":"# AR-033: Makefile 构建目标体系\n\n## Purpose\n\n本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 Makefile 构建目标体系，为 Docker 镜像构建、推送、验证、测试提供标准化的自动化命令。该 Makefile 是 AgentCube 容器化工作流的核心入口，支撑开发、CI/CD、生产环境的镜像生命周期管理。\n\n目标是：\n\n1. **构建自动化** - 提供统一的 `make` 命令简化 Docker 镜像构建流程，减少手动操作错误\n2. **目标分层** - 支持全量构建 (`docker-build-all`) 和单组件构建 (`docker-build-workloadmanager` 等)，适应不同场景\n3. **推送标准化** - 统一镜像推送流程，自动关联 VERSION、COMMIT_SHA、DOCKER_TAG 多标签\n4. **集群集成** - 提供 Kind 集群加载目标 (`kind-load-all`)，支持本地开发测试\n5. **多架构支持** - 集成 Docker Buildx，支持 amd64、arm64 多架构镜像构建\n6. **质量门禁** - 内置镜像验证 (`docker-validate`) 和测试 (`docker-test`) 目标，确保镜像质量\n7. **清理工具** - 提供本地镜像清理目标 (`docker-clean`)，减少磁盘占用\n\n本提案基于 existing Makefile (仅包含 Docker 相关目标) 进行扩展，遵循 Makefile 最佳实践和 AR-032 Dockerfile 多阶段构建规范。\n\n## Scope\n\n**Module:** root  \n**Language:** Makefile  \n**Size:** M\n\n本 AR 包含：\n\n- **包含内容：**\n  - Makefile 根文件更新 - 扩展构建目标体系\n  - 构建目标 (build) - `docker-build-all`, `docker-build-*`\n  - 推送目标 (push) - `docker-push-all`, `docker-push-*`\n  - Kind 加载目标 (kind-load) - `kind-load-all`, `kind-load-*`\n  - 多架构目标 (buildx) - `docker-buildx-all`, `docker-buildx-*`\n  - 验证目标 (validate) - `docker-validate`, `docker-validate-*`\n  - 测试目标 (test) - `docker-test`, `docker-test-build`, `docker-test-runtime`\n  - 清理目标 (clean) - `docker-clean`\n  - 帮助目标 (help) - 打印可用目标和变量\n  - 配置变量 - `DOCKER_REGISTRY`, `DOCKER_TAG`, `VERSION`, `COMMIT_SHA`\n\n- **不包含内容：**\n  - Dockerfile 编写（由 AR-032 管理）\n  - Helm Chart 构建（由 AR-030 管理）\n  - CI/CD 流水线配置\n  - Go/Python 应用编译目标（已有独立 Makefile 或命令）\n\n## Current State Analysis\n\n### 现有 Makefile 状态\n\n根据根目录 `Makefile` (237 行)，当前已实现：\n\n**已有目标：**\n- `docker-build-all`, `docker-build-workloadmanager`, `docker-build-router`, `docker-build-picod` - 构建目标\n- `docker-push-all`, `docker-push-workloadmanager`, `docker-push-router`, `docker-push-picod` - 推送目标\n- `kind-load-all`, `kind-load-workloadmanager`, `kind-load-router`, `kind-load-picod` - Kind 加载目标\n- `docker-buildx-all`, `docker-buildx-workloadmanager`, `docker-buildx-router`, `docker-buildx-picod` - 多架构目标\n- `docker-clean` - 清理目标\n- `docker-validate`, `docker-validate-*` - 验证目标\n- `docker-test`, `docker-test-build`, `docker-test-runtime` - 测试目标\n- `help` - 帮助信息\n\n**已有变量：**\n- `DOCKER_REGISTRY` (默认：ghcr.io/volcano-sh)\n- `DOCKER_TAG` (默认：latest)\n- `VERSION` (从 git tag 获取)\n- `COMMIT_SHA` (从 git rev-parse 获取)\n\n**镜像命名：**\n- `WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE` = $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/workloadmanager\n- `ROUTER_IMAGE` = $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/router\n- `PICOD_IMAGE` = $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/picod\n\n### 差距分析\n\n当前 Makefile 已经比较完善，但根据 AR-033 的\"构建目标体系\"要求，需要：\n\n1. **目标文档化** - 缺少目标依赖关系图和执行顺序说明\n2. **测试脚本集成** - 验证脚本和测试脚本依赖外部文件 (`deployment/docker/test/validate.sh` 等)，需要确保这些文件存在\n3. **错误处理** - 部分目标缺少错误处理（如 `docker-clean` 使用 `-` 前缀忽略错误，但其他目标未处理）\n4. **可扩展性** - 新增组件时需要手动添加多个目标，缺少自动化生成机制\n5. **PHONY 声明** - 所有目标都已声明为 `.PHONY`，符合最佳实践\n\n### 参考设计规范\n\n根据 AR-032 proposal.md 和项目结构：\n\n**Makefile 要求：**\n- 支持三个组件：Workload Manager、Router、Picod\n- 镜像标签：latest, <commit-sha>, <version>\n- 基础镜像：distroless/static-debian11\n- 构建优化：多阶段构建，CGO_ENABLED=0\n\n**验证脚本要求：**\n- 检查镜像大小 (< 50MB)\n- 检查层数 (<= 5)\n- 检查非 root 用户\n- 检查端口暴露\n- 检查健康检查配置\n\n### 需要补充的文件\n\n根据 Makefile 中引用的脚本：\n\n1. `deployment/docker/test/validate.sh` - 镜像验证脚本\n2. `deployment/docker/test/build_test.sh` - 构建测试脚本\n3. `deployment/docker/test/runtime_test.sh` - 运行时测试脚本\n\n这些脚本当前不存在，需要创建。\n\n## Proposed Changes\n\n### 1. Makefile 目标体系结构\n\n```\nMakefile 目标层次结构\n\n1. 构建目标 (Build)\n   ├── docker-build-all           # 构建所有镜像\n   ├── docker-build-workloadmanager\n   ├── docker-build-router\n   └── docker-build-picod\n\n2. 推送目标 (Push)\n   ├── docker-push-all            # 推送所有镜像\n   ├── docker-push-workloadmanager\n   ├── docker-push-router\n   └── docker-push-picod\n\n3. Kind 加载目标 (Kind Load)\n   ├── kind-load-all              # 加载所有镜像到 Kind\n   ├── kind-load-workloadmanager\n   ├── kind-load-router\n   └── kind-load-picod\n\n4. 多架构目标 (Buildx)\n   ├── docker-buildx-all          # 多架构构建所有\n   ├── docker-buildx-workloadmanager\n   ├── docker-buildx-router\n   └── docker-buildx-picod\n\n5. 验证目标 (Validate)\n   ├── docker-validate            # 验证所有镜像\n   ├── docker-validate-workloadmanager\n   ├── docker-validate-router\n   └── docker-validate-picod\n\n6. 测试目标 (Test)\n   ├── docker-test                # 运行所有测试\n   ├── docker-test-build          # 构建测试\n   └── docker-test-runtime        # 运行时测试\n\n7. 清理目标 (Clean)\n   └── docker-clean               # 清理本地镜像\n\n8. 帮助目标 (Help)\n   └── help                       # 打印帮助信息\n```\n\n### 2. 现有 Makefile 保持不变\n\n当前 Makefile 已经实现了完整的目标体系，无需修改。重点补充缺失的脚本文件。\n\n### 3. 创建验证脚本\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# deployment/docker/test/validate.sh\n# Validate Docker image for size, layers, security, ports, healthcheck\n\nset -e\n\nIMAGE=\"${1:-}\"\n\nif [ -z \"$IMAGE\" ]; then\n    echo \"Usage: $0 <image-name>\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\necho \"Validating image: $IMAGE\"\necho \"\"\n\n# Check if image exists\nif ! docker image inspect \"$IMAGE\" > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n    echo \"✗ Image not found: $IMAGE\"\n    exit 1\nfi\necho \"✓ Image exists\"\n\n# Check image size (< 50MB)\nSIZE=$(docker image inspect \"$IMAGE\" --format='{{.Size}}')\nSIZE_MB=$((SIZE / 1024 / 1024))\nif [ $SIZE_MB -lt 50 ]; then\n    echo \"✓ Image size: ${SIZE_MB}MB (< 50MB)\"\nelse\n    echo \"✗ Image size: ${SIZE_MB}MB (>= 50MB)\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# Check layer count (<= 5)\nLAYERS=$(docker image history \"$IMAGE\" --format='{{.ID}}' | wc -l)\nif [ $LAYERS -le 5 ]; then\n    echo \"✓ Layer count: $LAYERS (<= 5)\"\nelse\n    echo \"✗ Layer count: $LAYERS (> 5)\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# Check non-root user\nUSER_SPEC=$(docker image inspect \"$IMAGE\" --format='{{.Config.User}}')\nif [ -n \"$USER_SPEC\" ] && [ \"$USER_SPEC\" != \"root\" ]; then\n    echo \"✓ Running as non-root: $USER_SPEC\"\nelse\n    echo \"✗ Running as root or no user specified\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# Check exposed ports\nPORTS=$(docker image inspect \"$IMAGE\" --format='{{json .Config.ExposedPorts}}')\nif echo \"$PORTS\" | grep -q \"8080\"; then\n    echo \"✓ Port 8080 exposed\"\nelse\n    echo \"✗ Port 8080 not exposed\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# Check healthcheck\nHEALTHCHECK=$(docker image inspect \"$IMAGE\" --format='{{json .Config.Healthcheck}}')\nif [ \"$HEALTHCHECK\" != \"null\" ] && [ -n \"$HEALTHCHECK\" ]; then\n    echo \"✓ Health check configured\"\nelse\n    echo \"✗ Health check not configured\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\necho \"\"\necho \"All validations passed!\"\n```\n\n### 4. 创建构建测试脚本\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# deployment/docker/test/build_test.sh\n# Test Docker image build process\n\nset -e\n\necho \"Running Docker build tests...\"\necho \"\"\n\n# Test 1: Check Dockerfile exists\necho \"Test 1: Checking Dockerfile existence...\"\nDOCKERFILES=(\n    \"deployment/docker/Dockerfile\"\n    \"deployment/docker/Dockerfile.router\"\n    \"deployment/docker/Dockerfile.picod\"\n)\n\nfor dockerfile in \"${DOCKERFILES[@]}\"; do\n    if [ -f \"$dockerfile\" ]; then\n        echo \"  ✓ $dockerfile exists\"\n    else\n        echo \"  ✗ $dockerfile not found\"\n        exit 1\n    fi\ndone\n\n# Test 2: Check Makefile targets\necho \"\"\necho \"Test 2: Checking Makefile targets...\"\nif make -n docker-build-all > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n    echo \"  ✓ docker-build-all target available\"\nelse\n    echo \"  ✗ docker-build-all target not found\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# Test 3: Check Docker daemon\necho \"\"\necho \"Test 3: Checking Docker daemon...\"\nif docker info > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n    echo \"  ✓ Docker daemon is running\"\nelse\n    echo \"  ✗ Docker daemon is not running\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# Test 4: Check buildx availability\necho \"\"\necho \"Test 4: Checking Docker buildx...\"\nif docker buildx version > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n    echo \"  ✓ Docker buildx is available\"\nelse\n    echo \"  ✗ Docker buildx not found (optional)\"\nfi\n\necho \"\"\necho \"All build tests passed!\"\n```\n\n### 5. 创建运行时测试脚本\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# deployment/docker/test/runtime_test.sh\n# Test Docker container runtime behavior\n\nset -e\n\necho \"Running Docker runtime tests...\"\necho \"\"\n\n# Test 1: Container starts successfully\necho \"Test 1: Testing container startup...\"\nTEST_IMAGE=\"${TEST_IMAGE:-ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager:latest}\"\n\nCONTAINER_ID=$(docker run -d --rm \"$TEST_IMAGE\" --help 2>/dev/null || true)\nif [ -n \"$CONTAINER_ID\" ]; then\n    echo \"  ✓ Container started successfully\"\n    docker stop \"$CONTAINER_ID\" 2>/dev/null || true\nelse\n    echo \"  ⚠ Container startup test skipped (image may not exist)\"\nfi\n\n# Test 2: Health check configuration\necho \"\"\necho \"Test 2: Checking health check configuration...\"\nHEALTHCHECK=$(docker image inspect \"$TEST_IMAGE\" --format='{{json .Config.Healthcheck}}' 2>/dev/null || echo \"null\")\nif [ \"$HEALTHCHECK\" != \"null\" ]; then\n    echo \"  ✓ Health check is configured\"\nelse\n    echo \"  ⚠ Health check not configured (image may not exist)\"\nfi\n\n# Test 3: Port exposure\necho \"\"\necho \"Test 3: Checking port exposure...\"\nPORTS=$(docker image inspect \"$TEST_IMAGE\" --format='{{json .Config.ExposedPorts}}' 2>/dev/null || echo \"null\")\nif echo \"$PORTS\" | grep -q \"8080\"; then\n    echo \"  ✓ Port 8080 is exposed\"\nelse\n    echo \"  ⚠ Port 8080 not exposed (image may not exist)\"\nfi\n\n# Test 4: Non-root user\necho \"\"\necho \"Test 4: Checking non-root user...\"\nUSER_SPEC=$(docker image inspect \"$TEST_IMAGE\" --format='{{.Config.User}}' 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nif [ -n \"$USER_SPEC\" ] && [ \"$USER_SPEC\" != \"root\" ]; then\n    echo \"  ✓ Running as non-root: $USER_SPEC\"\nelse\n    echo \"  ⚠ Root user or no user specified (image may not exist)\"\nfi\n\necho \"\"\necho \"All runtime tests completed!\"\n```\n\n### 6. 创建脚本执行权限\n\n```bash\nchmod +x deployment/docker/test/validate.sh\nchmod +x deployment/docker/test/build_test.sh\nchmod +x deployment/docker/test/runtime_test.sh\n```\n\n### 7. 目录结构\n\n```\ndeployment/docker/test/\n├── validate.sh        # 镜像验证脚本\n├── build_test.sh      # 构建测试脚本\n└── runtime_test.sh    # 运行时测试脚本\n```\n\n### 8. Makefile 更新（可选增强）\n\n如需增强 Makefile，可添加以下目标：\n\n```makefile\n# 新增：检查依赖\n.PHONY: check-docker\ncheck-docker:\n\t@command -v docker >/dev/null 2>&1 || { echo \"Docker is required but not installed.\"; exit 1; }\n\n.PHONY: check-buildx\ncheck-buildx:\n\t@docker buildx version >/dev/null 2>&1 || { echo \"Docker buildx is required.\"; exit 1; }\n\n# 新增：预检查\n.PHONY: prereqs\nprereqs: check-docker\n\t@echo \"✓ All prerequisites met\"\n\n# 新增：完整 CI 流程\n.PHONY: ci\nci: prereqs docker-test docker-build-all docker-validate\n\t@echo \"✓ CI pipeline completed\"\n```\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### 依赖影响\n\n| 依赖项 | 版本 | 用途 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| GNU Make | ≥3.81 | 构建自动化 |\n| Docker | ≥20.10 | 镜像构建和运行 |\n| Docker Buildx | ≥0.6 | 多架构构建（可选） |\n| Kind | ≥0.11 | 本地 Kubernetes 集群（可选） |\n| Bash | ≥4.0 | 脚本执行 |\n| Git | 任意 | 版本信息获取 |\n\n### 模块依赖关系\n\n```\nMakefile (根目录)\n├── deployment/docker/Dockerfile           # Workload Manager Dockerfile (AR-032)\n├── deployment/docker/Dockerfile.router    # Router Dockerfile (AR-032)\n├── deployment/docker/Dockerfile.picod     # Picod Dockerfile (AR-032)\n├── deployment/docker/test/validate.sh     # 镜像验证脚本 (本 AR 新增)\n├── deployment/docker/test/build_test.sh   # 构建测试脚本 (本 AR 新增)\n└── deployment/docker/test/runtime_test.sh # 运行时测试脚本 (本 AR 新增)\n```\n\n### 向后兼容性\n\n- 现有 Makefile 目标保持不变\n- 新增脚本文件不影响现有功能\n- 环境变量使用默认值，向后兼容\n\n### 测试影响\n\n- 需要验证 Makefile 目标可正常执行\n- 需要验证脚本文件有执行权限\n- 需要验证测试脚本在 Docker 缺失时优雅降级\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n### 方案 1: 使用 Task (taskfile.dev) 替代 Make\n\n**优点:**\n- 更现代的语法，支持 YAML\n- 跨平台兼容性更好\n- 支持任务依赖和并行执行\n\n**缺点:**\n- 需要额外安装 Task 工具\n- 增加学习成本\n- Make 在项目中的使用已经很普遍\n\n**决策:** 继续使用 Makefile，保持简单和普遍兼容性。\n\n### 方案 2: 使用 Shell 脚本替代 Makefile\n\n**优点:**\n- 更灵活，支持复杂逻辑\n- 无需学习 Make 语法\n\n**缺点:**\n- 缺少目标依赖管理\n- 并行执行能力弱\n- 不适合管理大量相关命令\n\n**决策:** Makefile 更适合管理构建目标体系。\n\n### 方案 3: 每个组件独立 Makefile\n\n**优点:**\n- 组件解耦\n- 各自维护构建逻辑\n\n**缺点:**\n- 重复配置（变量、公共目标）\n- 全量构建需要多次调用\n- 增加维护成本\n\n**决策:** 使用根目录统一 Makefile，通过目标前缀区分组件。\n\n### 方案 4: 完全依赖 CI/CD（本地无构建）\n\n**优点:**\n- 本地环境简化\n- 构建一致性高\n\n**缺点:**\n- 开发调试效率低\n- 依赖网络和服务可用性\n\n**决策:** 保留本地构建能力，CI/CD 作为补充。\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Makefile 目标测试\n\n1. **目标可用性测试** - 验证所有 `make` 目标可被调用\n2. **依赖关系测试** - 验证目标依赖正确（如 `docker-build-all` 依赖各组件构建）\n3. **变量覆盖测试** - 验证环境变量可正确覆盖默认值\n\n### 脚本测试\n\n1. **验证脚本测试** - 对合法镜像验证通过，对非法镜像验证失败\n2. **构建测试** - 验证 Dockerfile、Docker daemon、buildx 检测有效\n3. **运行时测试** - 验证容器启动、健康检查、端口检测有效\n\n### 集成测试\n\n1. **完整流程测试** - `make docker-build-all` → `make docker-validate` → `make kind-load-all`\n2. **错误处理测试** - Docker 未运行时给出友好提示\n3. **清理测试** - `make docker-clean` 正确清理镜像\n\n### 测试覆盖目标\n\n- Makefile 目标：100%（所有目标可执行）\n- 验证脚本：100%（所有检查项有效）\n- 构建测试：100%（所有前置检查有效）\n- 运行时测试：100%（所有运行时检查有效）\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] Makefile 所有目标可正常执行 (`make help` 列出所有目标)\n- [ ] `make docker-build-all` 成功构建三个镜像\n- [ ] `make docker-push-all` 成功推送镜像（需有推送权限）\n- [ ] `make kind-load-all` 成功加载镜像到 Kind 集群\n- [ ] `make docker-validate` 成功验证镜像\n- [ ] `make docker-test` 成功运行所有测试\n- [ ] `make docker-clean` 成功清理本地镜像\n- [ ] `make docker-buildx-all` 成功构建多架构镜像（需 buildx）\n- [ ] 验证脚本 (`validate.sh`) 可独立执行\n- [ ] 构建测试脚本 (`build_test.sh`) 可独立执行\n- [ ] 运行时测试脚本 (`runtime_test.sh`) 可独立执行\n- [ ] 所有脚本具有执行权限\n- [ ] 文档完整（帮助信息、使用说明）\n\n## Dependencies\n\n### 必需依赖\n- GNU Make ≥3.81\n- Docker ≥20.10\n- Bash ≥4.0\n- Git\n\n### 可选依赖\n- Docker Buildx ≥0.6（多架构构建）\n- Kind ≥0.11（本地 Kubernetes 测试）\n\n### 被依赖\n- AR-032 (Dockerfile 多阶段构建) - 提供 Dockerfile\n- AR-030 (Helm Chart) - 镜像用于 Helm 部署\n\n## Migration Notes\n\n### 从现有 Makefile 迁移\n\n当前 Makefile 已经是最新状态，无需迁移。新增的脚本文件是 Makefile 目标的依赖，需要创建。\n\n### 破坏性变更\n无 - 仅补充缺失的脚本文件。\n\n### 行为变更\n- `make docker-validate` 从失败变为成功（验证脚本存在后）\n- `make docker-test` 从失败变为成功（测试脚本存在后）\n\n## Open Questions\n\n1. 是否需要支持 Windows 环境下的 Makefile 等价物（如 PowerShell 脚本）？\n2. 是否需要集成镜像签名（cosign）到 Makefile 目标？\n3. 是否需要支持远程 Docker daemon（DOCKER_HOST 环境变量）？\n\n## References\n\n- `Makefile` - 现有 Makefile 文件\n- `changes/AR-032/proposal.md` - Dockerfile 多阶段构建提案\n- `deployment/docker/Dockerfile` - Workload Manager Dockerfile\n- `deployment/docker/Dockerfile.router` - Router Dockerfile\n- `deployment/docker/Dockerfile.picod` - Picod Dockerfile\n- GNU Make Best Practices: https://www.gnu.org/software/make/manual/make.html\n- Docker Makefile Best Practices: https://docs.docker.com/build/building/best-practices/\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775882268593,"end":1775882268605}}}}
